{"type": "article", "id": 2486, "title": "Vitamin 2014 最新家居系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-22T08:39:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232509oEZhWLfXSA1GMVeK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t东敦伦设计品牌 Vitamin 日前带来了他们的 2014 最新家居系列作品，包括挂钩、吧椅、台灯、镜子等。这个系列的珍贵之处在于由纯手工制作完成，灵感来源于陀螺的挂钩用天然橡木打造，被赋予圆润的外形，避免衣物被钩丝，K Lamp 台灯独特的造型使得光源照射到顶部再被反射下来更显温暖。目前，Vitamin 2014 最新家居系列作品正在<a href=\"http://www.londondesignfestival.com/\" target=\"_blank\">伦敦设计节</a>上展出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232507aPkLSm8bgrIt1nA2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232508tj7A8rNzG6lMnCha.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232508xXhQ5LG6O1fSBJ70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232508WVt8lYPr9IkmJa2n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.071875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}